594	                className="flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg border border-[#A8A29E] bg-[#F5F3EF] px-3 py-1.5 font-medium font-new-sans text-[#44403C] text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-[#EDE9E3]"
